ğŸ§¾ Chemical Datasheet â€“ Potassium Perchlorate
Chemical Name: Potassium Perchlorate
Formula / Structural Diagram: KClOâ‚„ (ionic compound: Kâº + ClOâ‚„â»)
CAS #: 7778-74-7
