ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ”¬ Lab Use Notes
â— PPE: Chemical-resistant gloves, safety goggles, lab coat, dust mask/respirator.
â— Handling: Extremely toxic and strong oxidizer. Avoid all exposure to dust and ingestion.
